  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::InspectorNote
  Notes: 'How to integrate:

    1. Just enable whatever unlocked cards there are
    based on what cards are supposed to be unlocked and disable the rest

    2.
    Then enable whatever remaining locked cards left

    3. Profit. Stonk


    ----

    Disclaimer:
    I only did the card grab preview and card press effect only


    ----

    Also
    set your UI Canvas to Scale with screen size and set reference to 1920 x 1080
    otherwise scaling will screw up your UI '
